Package io.github.qubitpi.athena.file.identifier

Class FileNameAndUploadedTimeBasedIdGenerator

java.lang.Object
io.github.qubitpi.athena.file.identifier.FileNameAndUploadedTimeBasedIdGenerator
All Implemented Interfaces:
FileIdGenerator, Function<File,String>
@Immutable @ThreadSafe public class FileNameAndUploadedTimeBasedIdGenerator extends Object implements FileIdGenerator
FileNameAndUploadedTimeBasedIdGenerator generates file ID as hashes using hashing algorithm.

FileNameAndUploadedTimeBasedIdGenerator outputs the file ID by generating a fixed-length hash value based on the filename and the time (ms-precision) on which apply(File) is invoked an and then base-64 encoding that hash value as the final file ID
